{
  "chapter": 66,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十六回 神秘的通道\n\n吕三在简陋木屋中向齐小燕揭示计划：他故意将精锐调往胡集以误导班察巴那，同时暗藏独孤痴。吕三要齐小燕嫁给独孤痴以达成某种交易。随后吕三打开木柜秘门，进入一个辉煌富丽的黄金世界，引见三位代号剑客——四号、十四号、二十四号。\n\n吕三依次派四号和十四号进入一条阴暗的神秘通道刺杀目标，两人均一去不返。最后二十四号接令，但他先与吕三进行一场关于杀人原则的对话：他为吃饭而杀人，有绝不破例的规矩，接受吕三的十足纯金定金后走入通道。\n\n齐小燕与吕三讨论二十四号的原则——明知必死仍守规矩收金。吕三表达对这种有原则之人的尊敬。随后二人共进晚餐，齐小燕追问杀人是否也需要亲手去做的乐趣，吕三不答。最后吕三走入通道，揭示通道实为三十三曲的迷宫，齐小燕若直走必碰壁。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在班察巴那一定已经接到了他属下的报告，已经知道我已经将精锐全部调集到‘胡集’去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一定认为我也在‘胡集’。因为我恨小方，正好将计就计，利用这次机会亲自将小方置之于死地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "班察巴那一向算无遗策，但是我保证他这次一定会算错一件事。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "他一定不会相信独孤痴真的在我这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "独孤痴真的在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你真的要我嫁给他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "婚姻是件很奇怪的事，有时不仅是男女间的结合而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "那是为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是种手段。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "贫穷人家的子女以婚姻作手段，来取得以后生活的保障；富贵人家的子女也会以婚姻作手段，来增加自己的地位和权力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你自己也该知道，我要你嫁给独孤痴，对你对我都一样有好处。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "但是我一直到现在还没有见到他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你想见他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "好，你跟我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "他们都是我的好帮手，也都是一等一的剑客。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "可惜他们在我这里只有代号，没有名字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我要他们在这里待命，只因为我也要他们去杀一个人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "杀谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_si_hao",
      "text": "你一直往前走，走到尽头处，也有一道门。门是虚掩着的，有个人就坐在门后，只要一开门就可以看见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_si_hao",
      "text": "我要你去杀了他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_si_hao",
      "text": "现在就去。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我现在就去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "我要做的事，一定要做成。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "四号做不成，现在只有让你去做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "你去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我从七岁学剑，十三岁时学剑未成，就已学会杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "而且我真的杀了一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "你十三岁的时候，就已将你家乡最凶横的陆屠户刺杀在当地最热闹的菜市口。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "可是我这一生中杀的人并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "因为我从不愿惹事生非，也从来没有跟别人结仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "最主要的是，我根本就不喜欢杀人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "你杀人只不过为了要活下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我杀人只不过为了要吃饭而已。每个人都要吃饭，我也是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "为了吃饭而杀人虽然不是件愉快的事，但是另外还有一些人为了吃饭而做出的事比我做的事更痛苦。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我既然为了要吃饭而杀人，所以我每次杀人都要有代价的。从来都没有一次例外。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你虽然在我身份暴露，被人追杀时收容了我，可是你也不能例外。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你当然也应该知道我杀人的价钱。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "我早就准备好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "我也知道你的规矩，杀人前只要先付一半。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "这块黄金应该已经够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "这已经足够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "这块金子不但成色极纯，而且金质极好，一般市面上是绝对买不到的。只不过一个人如果死了，黄金对他又有什么用？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "我还要求你一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_shi_si_hao",
      "speaker_name": "二十四号",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "如果我死了，求你千万不要为我洗手上香，因为你已经付出了代价。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "这个人真是个怪人。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "他好像已经明白这一去非死不可，而且也明明知道一个人死了之后，成分再纯的黄金对他都没有用了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "但他却偏偏还是要先收下你这块黄金，他这是为了什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "这是为了他的原则。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "原则？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "原则就是规矩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "他自知必死也要去做这件事。既然要去做就得先收下这块黄金，因为这是他的规矩。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "一个有原则的人，规矩是绝不可破的。不管他是死是活都一样。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你觉得这种人是笨？还是聪明？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我只知道现在这种人已经越来越少了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你是否很喜欢这种人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "那么你为什么还要他去送死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你怎么知道他是去送死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你怎么知道死的不是我要他去杀的那个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "莫非你已经知道我要他杀的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我们好像应该吃饭了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "吃饭？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "你要吃饭？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "吃饭并不是件怪事，每个人都要吃饭的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "应该吃饭的时候就要吃饭，不管事情怎么样发展都要吃饭。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "这就是你的原则？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "今天我们吃了虾和蟹，只有自己亲手剥虾和蟹，才能真正领略到吃虾和蟹的乐趣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "只有用清茶洗手，才能洗掉手上的腥气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "杀人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "杀人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "杀人是不是也跟吃虾和蟹一样？也要自己亲手去杀，才能领略到其中的乐趣？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "那就得看了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "看什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "看你要杀的是什么人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "有些人你不妨要别人去杀，有些人却一定非要自己亲手去杀不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "杀完了之后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "如果你亲手去杀，杀完了之后要用什么才能洗掉你手上的血腥气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你最好不要一直再往前走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "齐小燕",
      "listener": "char_lv_san",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "因为这条通道不是直的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "这条通道一共有三十三曲。如果你一直往前走，一定会碰到墙上，碰扁你的鼻子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_san",
      "speaker_name": "吕三",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我知道你也许不信。从外面看，这条通道确实是笔直通到底的，如果你不信，不妨试一试。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    }
